      "text": "So he vouched-- he was in uniform.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was in the French and English army, French army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the camp commandant took his word for the fact that we would not be a burden to the state, that we would be able to nourish ourselves outside, and he let us go.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took us back to Grasse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let's stop here and change the tape.",
